index 2db769f..14d4ead 100644
--- a/CHANGES.rst
+++ b/CHANGES.rst
@@ -28,6 +28,8 @@ Unreleased
 
 -   Enable deferred evaluation of annotations with
     ``from __future__ import annotations``. :pr:`2270`
+-   ``click.edit()``'s ``filename`` parameter can be an iterable of
